name: MentalDisordersSNOMEDCT
title: Mental Disorders SNOMED CT
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values identifies patients who have a mental disorder.),(Data Element Scope: The intent of this data element is to identify patients who have a mental disorder.  Using the Quality Data Model, this data element maps to the Diagnosis category.),(Inclusion Criteria: Only include codes which represent a mental disorder.  Codes used are to be SNOMED-CT only.),(Exclusion Criteria: Exclude codes that do not meet the inclusion criteria.)
